WEBVTT

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:38.280
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:41.289
[Episode 17]

00:01:46.470 --> 00:01:47.750
[Hailan University]

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:49.580
[Aren't they friends?]

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:51.420
[So sweet.]

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:04.040
[Knock and then come in]

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:04.960
Who are you?

00:02:05.120 --> 00:02:07.520
Don't you know "first come, first served"?

00:02:09.979 --> 00:02:10.900
Chen Zhihan.

00:02:11.580 --> 00:02:13.580
You knew clearly I like Tong Xiaole,

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:15.040
yet you hypocritically
gave me his WeChat ID

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.160
and hid the fact that you two are dating!

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:19.290
Did you have to humiliate me like that?

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:20.320
I'm sorry.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.320
I indeed was in the wrong.

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:23.320
He and I indeed...

00:02:30.920 --> 00:02:33.190
Don't even mention Yi Lan.

00:02:33.210 --> 00:02:34.540
She's driving me crazy.

00:02:35.950 --> 00:02:38.040
And our high school classmate, Luo Ningzi.

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:38.650
Do you still remember her?

00:02:38.650 --> 00:02:40.480
Her family used to be pretty rich, right?

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:43.320
Later, for some unknown reason,
they went bankrupt.

00:02:43.320 --> 00:02:45.180
Now she's busy with socializing,

00:02:46.070 --> 00:02:47.480
networking everywhere for money.

00:02:47.480 --> 00:02:49.010
What are you talking about?

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:53.400
Why did you eavesdrop on my call?

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:02.350
So impolite.

00:03:02.790 --> 00:03:03.870
Hey, don't run!

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:04.440
Lan.

00:03:06.570 --> 00:03:07.500
Just ignore her.

00:03:08.070 --> 00:03:09.720
Please don't take it to heart.

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:11.450
She was just spreading rumors.

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:12.980
What have you been up to lately?

00:03:12.980 --> 00:03:15.440
Let's have a meal together
when you're free.

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:16.390
Tonight,

00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:18.920
would you like to come to the restaurant
where I work part-time to watch me play?

00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:19.450
My treat.

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:20.480
Sure.

00:03:20.620 --> 00:03:21.040
Mm.

00:03:21.829 --> 00:03:22.430
It's fine.

00:03:22.760 --> 00:03:24.090
I'm going to rehearsal.

00:03:27.930 --> 00:03:29.590
Always eating skewers is a bit boring.

00:03:29.590 --> 00:03:30.200
Hot pot?

00:03:31.010 --> 00:03:32.390
Something like that.

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:34.040
Our bro came.

00:03:35.160 --> 00:03:37.220
Weren't you in the restroom?
That took forever.

00:03:37.220 --> 00:03:38.200
Sorry, let's go.

00:03:38.579 --> 00:03:39.290
Let's go.

00:03:39.630 --> 00:03:39.740
So, where to?

00:03:39.740 --> 00:03:40.600
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:42.530
We haven't decided what to eat yet.

00:03:46.829 --> 00:03:47.720
Lan!

00:03:50.510 --> 00:03:52.579
Why are you wearing my coat?

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:53.500
Why did you...

00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:55.300
Why did you come outside to wait?

00:03:55.850 --> 00:03:57.860
Why are you wearing my coat?

00:03:58.160 --> 00:04:00.160
Riding the electric scooter at night
is cold.

00:04:00.160 --> 00:04:01.960
I was worried you might get cold.

00:04:02.160 --> 00:04:03.320
So thoughtful.

00:04:04.290 --> 00:04:05.210
Let me tell you,

00:04:05.230 --> 00:04:07.320
Ning played really well today.

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:08.040
I'm thinking,

00:04:08.040 --> 00:04:09.070
maybe if I get a chance,

00:04:09.070 --> 00:04:10.600
I could
find a part-time job like this too.

00:04:10.600 --> 00:04:12.400
It might help me improve myself.

00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:14.600
I don't think...

00:04:14.780 --> 00:04:15.440
you need to.

00:04:15.670 --> 00:04:16.230
Why?

00:04:16.640 --> 00:04:17.310
Because...

00:04:18.190 --> 00:04:20.600
my girlfriend is already super amazing.

00:04:20.640 --> 00:04:21.600
Really?

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:22.790
Of course.

00:04:23.750 --> 00:04:25.280
Did Chen Fan come today too?

00:04:25.860 --> 00:04:26.960
I don't know. Why?

00:04:27.110 --> 00:04:28.700
I think I saw him.

00:04:29.220 --> 00:04:30.510
How has he been lately?

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:32.520
I think

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:35.780
he should have the ability
to sort himself out.

00:04:35.780 --> 00:04:36.790
But as for you,

00:04:37.180 --> 00:04:39.080
can you take better care of yourself?

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.000
What about me?

00:04:41.110 --> 00:04:42.159
How come I heard

00:04:42.450 --> 00:04:44.710
someone has been bullying you at school?

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:45.920
It's nothing.

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:46.909
I can handle it myself.

00:04:46.909 --> 00:04:48.980
If someone bullies you,
that's a serious matter!

00:04:48.980 --> 00:04:50.280
From now on, no matter what happens,

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:51.210
you must tell me.

00:04:51.220 --> 00:04:51.720
Got it?

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:52.550
Okay, okay.

00:04:52.550 --> 00:04:54.610
I'll tell you everything from now on.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.320
Are you tired?

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:31.920
No.

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:32.550
♪ The story begins with hand in hand ♪

00:05:32.550 --> 00:05:33.310
Really?

00:05:33.470 --> 00:05:34.180
Really.

00:05:34.930 --> 00:05:36.090
Occupied. Occupied. Occupied.

00:05:36.090 --> 00:05:36.600
Occupied. Occupied. Occupied.

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:38.620
♪ For no reason at all ♪

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:41.490
♪ I just want to walk with you ♪

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:42.760
See? You got up late.
The practice rooms are all occupied.

00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:46.580
♪ Simply until we grow old ♪

00:05:47.690 --> 00:05:51.490
♪ Every warm touch that drew us closer ♪

00:05:52.140 --> 00:05:52.159
♪ Was nothing but a dream ♪

00:05:52.159 --> 00:05:53.430
It's this piece.

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:54.650
They play really well.

00:05:54.650 --> 00:05:55.110
♪ So many sunrises and sunsets ♪

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:55.790
Mm.

00:05:57.010 --> 00:05:58.380
Not as good as your playing.

00:05:58.380 --> 00:06:02.220
♪ Have changed our original hearts ♪

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:06.010
♪ By not thinking about it or guessing ♪

00:06:06.390 --> 00:06:09.340
♪ I thought I could break free ♪

00:06:09.510 --> 00:06:15.830
♪ Time has shown
I'm not as carefree as I imagined ♪

00:06:18.090 --> 00:06:22.050
♪ I still can't forget the tenderness
you gave me that year ♪

00:06:22.130 --> 00:06:25.790
♪ Exhausting all my strength,
I still can't fool myself ♪

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:29.320
♪ Your place is still here ♪

00:06:29.470 --> 00:06:33.270
♪ No one else can take it ♪

00:06:34.070 --> 00:06:37.630
♪ Let me treat it as just a heavy rain ♪

00:06:37.860 --> 00:06:42.470
♪ Gradually, the memories we've built
become clear ♪

00:06:42.630 --> 00:06:46.970
♪ All composed into a song ♪

00:06:48.270 --> 00:06:51.530
♪ It's still so beautiful ♪

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:52.790
You passed.

00:06:53.870 --> 00:06:54.430
Yes!

00:06:58.080 --> 00:06:59.480
Thank you, Professor Ye.

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:01.840
But your technique
still needs improvement.

00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:03.840
From now on, practice 4 hours every day.

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:05.640
I guarantee I will complete the task.

00:07:05.640 --> 00:07:07.570
I'll get going then, Professor Ye.

00:07:12.520 --> 00:07:13.320
Professor Ye,

00:07:14.260 --> 00:07:16.680
I want to... ask you a question.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:17.810
Go ahead.

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:21.180
How are things between you

00:07:21.310 --> 00:07:22.280
and Shan now?

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.290
Shan is my brother.

00:07:25.320 --> 00:07:27.120
I've known him since childhood.

00:07:27.180 --> 00:07:29.090
So I care about how he's doing.

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:30.960
I can tell

00:07:31.530 --> 00:07:33.390
he has always loved you very much.

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:35.520
So, what...

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:37.140
are...

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:38.280
your thoughts?

00:07:46.640 --> 00:07:47.640
Sometimes,

00:07:48.159 --> 00:07:51.220
2 people who love each other deeply
can still separate.

00:07:56.870 --> 00:07:58.800
It's best if you don't understand.

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:00.480
Focus on practicing.

00:08:00.520 --> 00:08:00.960
Mm?

00:08:11.500 --> 00:08:12.970
What makes you so happy?

00:08:13.400 --> 00:08:15.310
Xiaole!

00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:18.600
I passed Professor Ye's interview!

00:08:18.740 --> 00:08:19.280
Really?

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:20.310
Yes!

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:22.770
Congratulations!

00:08:22.830 --> 00:08:24.070
But

00:08:24.190 --> 00:08:26.080
she said my technique isn't good enough.

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:27.060
I need special training.

00:08:27.060 --> 00:08:28.620
At least 4 hours every day.

00:08:28.760 --> 00:08:31.950
That means the time I spend with you
will be a little bit less.

00:08:31.950 --> 00:08:32.830
It's okay.

00:08:32.850 --> 00:08:34.600
I'll be very busy too.

00:08:34.950 --> 00:08:38.640
A professor in my department helped me
get a part-time job at a newspaper.

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:39.950
I need to report for duty next week.

00:08:39.950 --> 00:08:40.760
A newspaper?

00:08:40.760 --> 00:08:41.159
Mm.

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:42.190
Do you like it?

00:08:43.570 --> 00:08:44.450
Well...

00:08:45.400 --> 00:08:47.240
I wouldn't say I like it.

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:48.280
But

00:08:48.550 --> 00:08:49.750
I want to give it a try.

00:08:49.860 --> 00:08:50.460
It's okay.

00:08:50.520 --> 00:08:52.250
I think you'll do great.

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:57.440
-I'm so happy!
-You're so happy.

00:09:00.070 --> 00:09:00.920
I have a question.

00:09:00.920 --> 00:09:01.280
Mm?

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:04.530
Why did someone say
that even if 2 people love each other,

00:09:04.530 --> 00:09:06.060
they might still separate?

00:09:06.520 --> 00:09:08.280
We love each other very much now,

00:09:08.280 --> 00:09:10.430
but I think we'll never be apart.

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:12.790
Someone?

00:09:13.400 --> 00:09:14.160
Who?

00:09:15.330 --> 00:09:16.750
Just someone.

00:09:18.430 --> 00:09:19.430
Her surname is Ye.

00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:20.540
She's a professor.

00:09:20.540 --> 00:09:21.280
Right?

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:22.430
Mm.

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:24.040
Tell me, why?

00:09:24.430 --> 00:09:27.030
Professor Ye and Shan
clearly love each other.

00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:28.550
Everyone knows that

00:09:28.790 --> 00:09:29.920
except themselves.

00:09:31.670 --> 00:09:33.040
Their relationship

00:09:33.130 --> 00:09:34.590
is indeed quite complicated.

00:09:34.590 --> 00:09:35.450
But I think

00:09:35.520 --> 00:09:37.430
if we were in that situation,

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:38.920
it wouldn't be like that.

00:09:38.920 --> 00:09:40.360
I would definitely take the initiative
and tell you

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:42.160
I like you very, very, very much.

00:09:42.560 --> 00:09:44.040
♪ Boba tea with sugar means I like you ♪

00:09:44.040 --> 00:09:46.050
And I like you
very, very, very, very much.

00:09:46.050 --> 00:09:47.390
♪ Warm palms ♪

00:09:48.010 --> 00:09:49.520
♪ The pleasant smell of love ♪

00:09:49.870 --> 00:09:49.920
♪ I sync my playlist with yours
in secret ♪

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:50.450
Besides,

00:09:50.520 --> 00:09:52.130
you'll never have that chance
in this lifetime.

00:09:52.130 --> 00:09:53.140
♪ Let our hearts beat in sync ♪

00:09:53.210 --> 00:09:53.360
♪ Let us breathe in sync ♪

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:53.790
Okay.

00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:57.280
♪ You are everything I want ♪

00:09:57.280 --> 00:09:58.120
Faster.

00:09:58.550 --> 00:09:59.480
Watch the tempo.

00:10:01.640 --> 00:10:02.070
Stop.

00:10:02.950 --> 00:10:03.550
Look here.

00:10:10.790 --> 00:10:11.400
Again.

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:18.400
Ms. Ye, you're amazing.

00:10:18.570 --> 00:10:21.360
You really can predict
every mistake I'll make.

00:10:22.180 --> 00:10:24.040
You're so happy
even after being criticized.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:25.120
You're the first one.

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:27.240
I started later than others.

00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:29.600
Just point out anything I do wrong.

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:34.410
Have you ever thought
about studying abroad?

00:10:34.920 --> 00:10:36.280
Studying abroad?

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:38.040
I've never thought about it.

00:10:38.040 --> 00:10:39.770
I think you should give it a try.

00:10:39.850 --> 00:10:42.280
Go to different places
and listen to different music styles.

00:10:42.280 --> 00:10:44.340
It will also help your future career.

00:10:45.160 --> 00:10:46.280
You mean...

00:10:46.430 --> 00:10:47.630
an exchange student?

00:10:49.270 --> 00:10:50.790
I think, with my current skill level,

00:10:50.790 --> 00:10:53.990
I'm not good enough yet
to compete with them for this spot.

00:10:54.400 --> 00:10:55.670
Maybe not before,

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:57.430
but you can try now.

00:10:57.980 --> 00:10:59.980
Actually, I have high hopes for you.

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:02.440
Thank you, Professor Ye.

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:05.920
Professor Ye,

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:07.320
it's my turn for a lesson.

00:11:07.880 --> 00:11:08.520
Come in.

00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:16.670
Stop.

00:11:17.760 --> 00:11:19.620
You've made a few mistakes today.

00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:22.540
I played it well when I practiced before.

00:11:22.790 --> 00:11:23.860
Maybe I'm just...

00:11:24.020 --> 00:11:25.040
a bit nervous now.

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:26.410
Don't make excuses.

00:11:27.160 --> 00:11:29.290
Have you been practicing 4 hours a day?

00:11:29.850 --> 00:11:31.360
I've been doing part-time performances.

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.040
Counting the performance time,

00:11:33.040 --> 00:11:33.760
it's enough.

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:35.290
Then what do you usually do?

00:11:36.460 --> 00:11:37.990
Prepare for other classes.

00:11:41.280 --> 00:11:42.170
Luo Ningzi,

00:11:42.920 --> 00:11:45.250
there is only one spot
for the exchange student program.

00:11:45.250 --> 00:11:47.290
Talented people are everywhere.

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.600
If you don't give it your all,

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:51.560
how can you compete with others?

00:11:51.730 --> 00:11:52.370
I...

00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:56.920
I understand, Professor Ye.

00:11:56.920 --> 00:11:57.760
Next time,

00:11:57.760 --> 00:12:00.360
I'll definitely practice well
before coming.

00:12:00.520 --> 00:12:01.980
Let's stop here for today.

00:12:03.880 --> 00:12:04.880
Thank you, Ms. Ye.

00:12:10.330 --> 00:12:12.060
Why are you waiting for me here?

00:12:12.550 --> 00:12:14.180
Why did you practice so long today?

00:12:14.180 --> 00:12:15.510
It's almost lights out.

00:12:15.780 --> 00:12:18.220
Professor Ye recommended that I apply
for the exchange student program.

00:12:18.220 --> 00:12:19.950
She thinks pretty highly of me.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:21.640
I think I should give it a try.

00:12:22.650 --> 00:12:24.680
You definitely can do it.

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:26.250
Let's go.

00:12:33.950 --> 00:12:34.590
Ning.

00:12:35.070 --> 00:12:36.000
You're here too.

00:12:40.050 --> 00:12:41.650
You're preparing for IELTS?

00:12:43.070 --> 00:12:43.520
Yes.

00:12:43.590 --> 00:12:45.800
I plan to apply
for the exchange student program.

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:47.310
Do you plan to apply for it too?

00:12:47.310 --> 00:12:48.370
We can go together.

00:12:48.710 --> 00:12:50.440
I've been preparing all along.

00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:51.040
But

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:52.660
the requirements for exchange students
are very high.

00:12:52.660 --> 00:12:54.920
I'm afraid you can't meet them right now.

00:12:55.900 --> 00:12:57.140
I know.

00:12:57.280 --> 00:12:59.010
But I still want to give it a try.

00:12:59.520 --> 00:13:00.450
Then I advise you

00:13:00.550 --> 00:13:01.950
not to waste your energy.

00:13:04.050 --> 00:13:05.710
Why are you talking like that?

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:07.450
I thought you'd support me.

00:13:07.670 --> 00:13:09.200
I'm just telling the truth,

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:11.300
to save you from wasting time.

00:13:11.640 --> 00:13:13.040
I'm going to class first.

00:13:20.920 --> 00:13:21.560
Miss Luo.

00:13:26.780 --> 00:13:28.110
Um, I'm getting a call.

00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:30.020
You guys eat... eat first.

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:39.350
Here, Miss Luo.

00:13:40.070 --> 00:13:41.160
My art gallery

00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:42.420
will be opening soon.

00:13:42.550 --> 00:13:43.520
I must invite you

00:13:43.790 --> 00:13:45.070
to come and support it.

00:13:46.430 --> 00:13:47.040
I hope

00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:49.560
you can give a wonderful performance then.

00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:50.690
What do you say?

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:51.680
Mr. Guo,

00:13:51.700 --> 00:13:52.730
of course.

00:13:52.770 --> 00:13:55.430
Luo Ningzi and I
will definitely attend on time.

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:56.920
We won't let you down.

00:14:00.400 --> 00:14:01.160
Sit.

00:14:05.410 --> 00:14:06.070
Here, here.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:06.620
Mr. Guo,

00:14:06.790 --> 00:14:07.590
a toast to you.

00:14:08.300 --> 00:14:08.920
Miss Luo,

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:09.670
together?

00:14:09.850 --> 00:14:10.330
I...

00:14:11.310 --> 00:14:12.950
Um, she can't hold her liquor well.

00:14:12.950 --> 00:14:14.010
I'll drink for her.

00:14:21.100 --> 00:14:22.960
Mr. Guo, let me refill your glass.

00:14:25.130 --> 00:14:26.010
Eat. Eat.

00:14:26.170 --> 00:14:26.760
Yu,

00:14:26.940 --> 00:14:28.400
I'm not feeling very well.

00:14:28.640 --> 00:14:30.300
Please excuse me for a moment.

00:14:34.100 --> 00:14:35.100
Um...

00:14:35.460 --> 00:14:36.920
I'll go handle it.

00:14:37.000 --> 00:14:37.400
Here.

00:14:54.920 --> 00:14:55.590
Ning.

00:14:56.290 --> 00:14:57.690
He's a major sponsor.

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:00.620
He's funded many musicians
to study abroad.

00:15:00.990 --> 00:15:01.530
I am

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:03.160
working with him now.

00:15:03.270 --> 00:15:04.560
Only if we secure this deal

00:15:04.560 --> 00:15:07.160
will we have
more performance opportunities.

00:15:09.420 --> 00:15:10.550
So I hope you

00:15:10.810 --> 00:15:13.070
can talk more and express yourself more.

00:15:13.430 --> 00:15:14.400
Only this way

00:15:14.430 --> 00:15:16.160
can we seize this opportunity.

00:15:17.310 --> 00:15:18.310
What do you think?

00:15:18.550 --> 00:15:19.550
Mm, I understand.

00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:21.070
So...

00:15:29.380 --> 00:15:30.640
Are you okay, Miss Luo?

00:15:30.880 --> 00:15:32.400
I'm fine. Sorry.

00:15:32.920 --> 00:15:34.250
I'll drink a toast to you.

00:15:34.250 --> 00:15:35.700
Come on. I'll join you.

00:15:39.280 --> 00:15:39.760
Ning.

00:15:40.200 --> 00:15:41.330
Thank you for today.

00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:42.900
I know you're not a drinker,

00:15:42.900 --> 00:15:44.430
yet you drank so much for me.

00:15:44.430 --> 00:15:45.960
I'm really grateful to you.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:46.550
It's nothing.

00:15:46.550 --> 00:15:47.210
Be careful.

00:15:47.210 --> 00:15:47.880
Yu.

00:15:49.040 --> 00:15:50.770
Helping you is helping myself.

00:15:51.160 --> 00:15:53.620
We will definitely have more performances.

00:15:54.760 --> 00:15:56.820
Today, consider it overtime for you.

00:15:57.310 --> 00:15:58.940
I'll give you double overtime pay.

00:15:58.940 --> 00:16:00.000
Don't turn me down.

00:16:00.590 --> 00:16:01.960
Mm. Thanks.

00:16:02.790 --> 00:16:05.250
By the way,
is it okay for you to go back alone?

00:16:05.860 --> 00:16:06.300
Mm.

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:08.360
Okay. Be careful.

00:16:08.520 --> 00:16:09.120
Mm.

00:16:20.120 --> 00:16:21.650
We arrived at the same time.

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:23.240
Do you enjoy competing with me that much?

00:16:23.240 --> 00:16:24.400
I'm really not at my best today.

00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:25.000
Don't...

00:16:31.070 --> 00:16:32.100
Now, this is great.

00:16:32.100 --> 00:16:33.280
Neither of us can practice.

00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:35.190
I think Yi Lan is quite difficult.

00:16:35.640 --> 00:16:37.200
She always takes
other people's practice rooms.

00:16:37.200 --> 00:16:39.460
And she never holds back when she speaks.

00:16:40.260 --> 00:16:42.390
Come out and say it if you have the guts!

00:16:42.570 --> 00:16:43.050
Fine.

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:48.800
You two really are good friends.

00:16:49.140 --> 00:16:50.350
One lacks integrity,

00:16:50.750 --> 00:16:51.480
the other...

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:53.570
lacks integrity too.

00:16:53.570 --> 00:16:54.230
Luo Ningzi,

00:16:54.610 --> 00:16:57.070
who was that man
who sent you back last night?

00:16:57.160 --> 00:16:58.860
You kept throwing up
when you got back to the dorm.

00:16:58.860 --> 00:17:00.460
Why don't you just live off-campus?

00:17:00.460 --> 00:17:02.090
What does her business
have to do with you?

00:17:02.090 --> 00:17:03.690
How is it none of my business?

00:17:03.730 --> 00:17:05.060
It's all because of her.

00:17:05.510 --> 00:17:08.910
She's out there ruining the reputation
of us music students!

00:17:09.230 --> 00:17:11.160
What are you doing, all of you?

00:17:11.810 --> 00:17:13.829
You're bullying Tong Xiaole's girlfriend
because you can't have him.

00:17:13.829 --> 00:17:15.800
I'm telling you,
this is called bullying, you know?

00:17:15.800 --> 00:17:17.030
Wait, who are you?

00:17:17.270 --> 00:17:19.800
And what does this have to do
with Tong Xiaole?

00:17:21.780 --> 00:17:22.910
They're dormmates?

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:24.730
No wonder.

00:17:25.160 --> 00:17:27.089
Birds of a feather flock together.

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:28.660
A bunch of rabble.

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:30.140
No wonder you're at the bottom
of the major rankings.

00:17:30.140 --> 00:17:32.800
You've wasted all your time
on things like this.

00:17:33.770 --> 00:17:35.820
A bunch of underperforming students.

00:17:35.820 --> 00:17:37.220
What's there to show off?

00:17:37.920 --> 00:17:38.360
Also,

00:17:38.730 --> 00:17:40.530
who did you say lacks integrity?

00:17:41.570 --> 00:17:43.250
Try touching my cello again!

00:17:45.320 --> 00:17:47.930
Even my parents have never slapped me,
and you slapped me?

00:17:47.930 --> 00:17:48.840
You want to fight, huh?

00:17:48.840 --> 00:17:49.470
What are you doing?

00:17:49.470 --> 00:17:50.840
Go away!

00:17:50.840 --> 00:17:52.240
She slapped you! So what?

00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:55.140
What are you doing?

00:17:56.190 --> 00:17:57.030
Stop it!

00:17:57.920 --> 00:17:58.470
Let go!

00:17:58.900 --> 00:17:59.580
Let go!

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:00.710
Yi Lan!

00:18:00.770 --> 00:18:01.330
Yi Lan!

00:18:01.640 --> 00:18:02.400
Xiaole.

00:18:03.990 --> 00:18:06.160
Why did you have to fight
instead of talking things out?

00:18:06.160 --> 00:18:07.760
Your girlfriend started it!

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:09.050
I slapped her first.

00:18:09.470 --> 00:18:10.710
They touched my cello.

00:18:10.710 --> 00:18:11.790
Yi Lan was just trying to help me.

00:18:11.790 --> 00:18:12.550
See?

00:18:13.470 --> 00:18:14.640
She hangs out with Luo Ningzi.

00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:15.840
She can't be any good!

00:18:16.090 --> 00:18:17.850
Do your words have to be so harsh?

00:18:17.850 --> 00:18:19.850
Xiaole, let us handle it ourselves.

00:18:26.110 --> 00:18:26.800
You guys

00:18:27.470 --> 00:18:29.430
have seriously disrupted our practice.

00:18:29.430 --> 00:18:31.120
We came to the practice room first.

00:18:31.120 --> 00:18:32.550
You guys started this whole thing.

00:18:32.550 --> 00:18:34.350
Who has disturbed whom exactly?

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:36.160
And regarding Luo Ningzi's matters,

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:37.710
who are you to judge her?

00:18:38.600 --> 00:18:40.130
About what happened today,

00:18:40.400 --> 00:18:41.980
I will tell the student advisor.

00:18:41.980 --> 00:18:42.780
Just you wait.

00:18:44.230 --> 00:18:45.320
You can snitch,

00:18:45.320 --> 00:18:46.830
but we can't snitch, huh?

00:18:47.230 --> 00:18:47.920
Exactly.

00:18:48.320 --> 00:18:49.180
How old are you?

00:18:49.330 --> 00:18:51.160
When something happens,
all you do is run to the teacher.

00:18:51.160 --> 00:18:52.990
Coming to school is for learning.

00:18:52.990 --> 00:18:55.650
If you have the guts,
let's compete in our field.

00:18:58.530 --> 00:18:59.330
Fine.

00:18:59.840 --> 00:19:00.610
How?

00:19:00.950 --> 00:19:01.640
A duet.

00:19:01.780 --> 00:19:02.760
Yi Lan and me.

00:19:03.050 --> 00:19:03.730
The losers

00:19:04.230 --> 00:19:05.640
apologize publicly.

00:19:09.970 --> 00:19:10.900
Next Wednesday,

00:19:11.800 --> 00:19:13.260
see you in the auditorium.

00:19:17.350 --> 00:19:18.350
Is your foot okay?

00:19:20.520 --> 00:19:22.050
I sprained it a bit just now.

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:23.600
Can you still walk?

00:19:23.600 --> 00:19:24.400
Let me try.

00:19:26.710 --> 00:19:28.040
Be careful. Be careful.

00:19:28.560 --> 00:19:29.020
Come on.

00:19:30.260 --> 00:19:32.160
Let me take you to the infirmary.

00:19:37.170 --> 00:19:38.810
[Healthy Life
Take Control by Yourself]

00:19:38.810 --> 00:19:39.530
Doctor?

00:19:39.670 --> 00:19:41.350
[Treatment Room]

00:19:41.350 --> 00:19:42.080
Not here.

00:19:43.290 --> 00:19:44.290
Here. Be careful.

00:19:44.910 --> 00:19:45.550
Let's sit over here.

00:19:45.550 --> 00:19:49.660
[Healthy Life
Take Control by Yourself]

00:19:51.970 --> 00:19:52.160
[Healthy Life
Take Control by Yourself]

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:53.090
Here, let me see.

00:19:58.030 --> 00:19:58.400
Does it hurt?

00:19:58.400 --> 00:19:59.200
It hurts a lot.

00:20:00.440 --> 00:20:01.170
Does it hurt?

00:20:01.710 --> 00:20:02.640
A little.

00:20:03.670 --> 00:20:05.160
Wait a second.
I'll go get you an ice pack.

00:20:05.160 --> 00:20:05.620
No need.

00:20:05.880 --> 00:20:07.880
Let's just wait for the doctor here.

00:20:09.270 --> 00:20:10.560
Then put your foot like this.

00:20:10.560 --> 00:20:12.420
It helps with blood circulation.

00:20:19.600 --> 00:20:20.430
What's wrong?

00:20:23.800 --> 00:20:24.640
Tell me,

00:20:25.160 --> 00:20:26.400
why did Luo Ningzi

00:20:26.670 --> 00:20:27.950
ask me to do a duet?

00:20:29.690 --> 00:20:31.620
She didn't ask for your permission

00:20:31.950 --> 00:20:34.230
and dragged you into a competition.

00:20:34.920 --> 00:20:35.950
Aren't you angry?

00:20:38.950 --> 00:20:39.710
No.

00:20:40.230 --> 00:20:41.080
I just...

00:20:42.320 --> 00:20:43.720
don't quite understand.

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:44.480
Yi Lan.

00:20:46.310 --> 00:20:48.010
No matter what happens in the future,

00:20:48.010 --> 00:20:49.170
you can tell me.

00:20:49.480 --> 00:20:50.910
We can solve it together.

00:20:52.640 --> 00:20:53.400
Got it.

00:20:53.640 --> 00:20:55.640
But I can handle some things myself.

00:20:56.230 --> 00:20:56.780
Fine.

00:20:57.080 --> 00:20:58.920
If you can handle everything yourself,
you won't need me.

00:20:58.920 --> 00:21:00.510
Of course I need you.

00:21:00.750 --> 00:21:02.830
But you have your own things to do.

00:21:03.290 --> 00:21:05.500
And I don't want you
to become like my dad,

00:21:05.500 --> 00:21:06.990
worrying about me over everything.

00:21:06.990 --> 00:21:08.710
This isn't worrying.

00:21:09.300 --> 00:21:10.120
This is called

00:21:10.320 --> 00:21:12.050
the happiness of being needed.

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:13.320
Okay.

00:21:13.430 --> 00:21:15.670
Then I'll tell you every little thing
from now on.

00:21:15.670 --> 00:21:17.020
Just don't find me annoying.

00:21:17.020 --> 00:21:18.020
You'd better.

00:21:19.880 --> 00:21:20.510
Let me see.

00:21:21.230 --> 00:21:21.920
Is your head okay?

00:21:21.920 --> 00:21:22.750
It's fine.

00:21:23.640 --> 00:21:24.700
The doctor is here.

00:21:32.330 --> 00:21:32.850
Well...

00:21:33.130 --> 00:21:34.330
I'll let you two talk.

00:21:35.010 --> 00:21:36.810
I'll just go look for the doctor.

00:21:55.470 --> 00:21:56.950
About what happened just now,

00:21:56.950 --> 00:21:57.800
thank you.

00:21:59.700 --> 00:22:00.570
It's nothing.

00:22:01.840 --> 00:22:03.510
Aren't we best friends?

00:22:10.080 --> 00:22:11.160
Why did you...

00:22:11.640 --> 00:22:13.430
ask me to do a duet with you?

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:16.420
Why so many questions?

00:22:16.660 --> 00:22:17.460
To win.

00:22:19.140 --> 00:22:20.710
But you know clearly with my skill level,

00:22:20.710 --> 00:22:21.950
we can't beat them.

00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:23.640
With your current skill level,

00:22:23.640 --> 00:22:24.320
we can.

00:22:25.520 --> 00:22:27.420
Have I improved that much?

00:22:27.440 --> 00:22:28.740
Enough to beat them?

00:22:29.560 --> 00:22:31.620
I saw you in Professor Ye Mei's class.

00:22:31.710 --> 00:22:33.910
You certainly have what it takes to win.

00:22:35.090 --> 00:22:36.630
So all this time...

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:39.100
that is why?

00:22:41.140 --> 00:22:43.190
Haven't you been well-prepared all along?

00:22:43.190 --> 00:22:45.250
Are you worried I'll get ahead of you,

00:22:46.190 --> 00:22:47.250
or do you think

00:22:48.470 --> 00:22:50.160
I'm not qualified to compete with you?

00:22:50.160 --> 00:22:50.890
I don't know.

00:22:51.570 --> 00:22:52.250
I just know

00:22:52.330 --> 00:22:53.590
there's only one spot,

00:22:54.190 --> 00:22:55.120
and I can't lose.

00:22:55.420 --> 00:22:57.550
So you're worried I'll take your spot?

00:23:00.990 --> 00:23:01.560
Yes.

00:23:01.670 --> 00:23:02.510
I'm worried.

00:23:06.400 --> 00:23:09.450
You have the support of people around you
in everything you do.

00:23:09.450 --> 00:23:11.450
You have your own steadfast dreams.

00:23:12.080 --> 00:23:12.910
I envy you.

00:23:14.980 --> 00:23:15.680
And me?

00:23:16.240 --> 00:23:17.420
Because apples are good for health,

00:23:17.420 --> 00:23:18.450
I have to eat them all the time.

00:23:18.450 --> 00:23:19.470
Because I have a talent for the cello,

00:23:19.470 --> 00:23:21.470
I have to play the cello all the time.

00:23:21.680 --> 00:23:22.940
But you're different.

00:23:23.720 --> 00:23:25.890
You can do whatever makes you happy.

00:23:28.510 --> 00:23:29.820
So I also asked myself,

00:23:30.240 --> 00:23:31.380
what do I want?

00:23:37.160 --> 00:23:38.120
So...

00:23:39.060 --> 00:23:40.320
do you have the answer?

00:23:40.460 --> 00:23:41.220
No.

00:23:46.500 --> 00:23:47.650
I want to do well,

00:23:48.290 --> 00:23:49.490
but I want to know more

00:23:49.760 --> 00:23:52.490
whether I play the cello
for myself or for others.

00:23:54.340 --> 00:23:54.990
Ning.

00:23:56.850 --> 00:23:57.850
You know what?

00:23:59.970 --> 00:24:00.900
I envied you too.

00:24:03.430 --> 00:24:04.910
In my eyes,

00:24:06.760 --> 00:24:08.960
you've always been someone who shines.

00:24:10.340 --> 00:24:12.200
You've always been my role model.

00:24:14.930 --> 00:24:16.350
I want to tell you,

00:24:17.980 --> 00:24:19.610
whether it's for yourself

00:24:20.160 --> 00:24:21.400
or for others,

00:24:23.050 --> 00:24:24.930
you deserve what you like.

00:24:28.410 --> 00:24:29.770
I really like you.

00:24:32.470 --> 00:24:33.110
Thank you.

00:25:04.560 --> 00:25:09.240
[Student Practice Room 15]

00:25:19.640 --> 00:25:21.920
Do you want
to choose a piece for our duet?

00:25:24.670 --> 00:25:25.470
Sure.

00:25:32.970 --> 00:25:34.230
Do you have any ideas?

00:25:35.720 --> 00:25:36.740
Vivaldi.

00:25:36.760 --> 00:25:38.360
The Concerto for Two Cellos.

00:25:40.010 --> 00:25:41.460
Why this piece again?

00:25:42.160 --> 00:25:43.220
I want to play it...

00:25:43.300 --> 00:25:44.190
with you again.

00:25:45.760 --> 00:25:46.760
Let's try it then.

00:25:48.040 --> 00:25:49.160
You start first, as before.

00:25:49.160 --> 00:25:49.650
Mm.

00:25:50.160 --> 00:25:50.920
Don't go!

00:25:51.000 --> 00:25:52.130
Explain it clearly!

00:25:52.130 --> 00:25:53.320
Don't! Don't! Don't get physical!

00:25:53.320 --> 00:25:54.640
Explain it clearly!

00:25:54.640 --> 00:25:56.210
Let's talk this out properly.

00:25:56.210 --> 00:25:57.400
Can you let me explain it clearly?

00:25:57.400 --> 00:25:59.190
You can't solve the problem like this.

00:25:59.190 --> 00:26:01.030
Who do you think you are?

00:26:01.320 --> 00:26:03.450
Do you still want to get married or not?

00:26:08.060 --> 00:26:09.680
What is that man doing?

00:26:10.110 --> 00:26:11.570
How could he act like this?

00:26:11.670 --> 00:26:12.670
Look. Look. Look.

00:26:12.670 --> 00:26:13.900
What's going on?

00:26:13.930 --> 00:26:15.260
Look, you've messed up.

00:26:39.400 --> 00:26:40.200
What's wrong?

00:26:41.560 --> 00:26:42.960
I bumped into your cello?

00:26:43.130 --> 00:26:45.160
You should have watched
where you were going.

00:26:45.160 --> 00:26:46.230
Next time you go out,

00:26:46.230 --> 00:26:47.430
remember to bring your eyes.

00:26:47.430 --> 00:26:48.800
It was clearly you who bumped into me.

00:26:48.800 --> 00:26:50.530
Why are you blaming the victim?

00:26:52.160 --> 00:26:53.880
I really can't stand

00:26:53.880 --> 00:26:55.410
this pitiful look of yours.

00:26:55.490 --> 00:26:57.290
Who are you putting on a show for?

00:26:58.030 --> 00:26:59.640
Let's not wait until next week.

00:26:59.640 --> 00:27:00.240
Right now,

00:27:00.850 --> 00:27:01.910
let's have a match.

00:27:05.750 --> 00:27:06.610
Are you scared?

00:27:07.360 --> 00:27:08.150
Fine, let's do it.

00:27:08.150 --> 00:27:08.560
Come on.